00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:18,124
This was the roof.

671
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:31,524
The chamber was right under here.

672
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:32,886
Under our feet.

673
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:44,046
The doors were locked and
cyanide crystals, Zyklon-B,

